                    { title: t.sectors.s1_t[1], desc: lang === 'en' ? "Discarding flammable electrolytes, solid-state batteries are the 'ultimate solution' for transportation electrification. Authoritative data shows energy density can reach 500 Wh/kg, double current tech, solving safety pain points." : (lang === 'zh-Hans' ? "舍弃易燃电解质，固态电池是交通电气化的「最终解答」。权威数据显示其能量密度可达 500 Wh/kg，是现有技术的 2 倍，且彻底解决安全性痛点。" : "捨棄易燃電解質，固態電池是交通電氣化的「最終解答」。權威數據顯示其能量密度可達 500 Wh/kg，是現有技術的 2 倍，且徹底解決安全性痛點。"), sources: [{ label: "QuantumScape White Paper", url: "https://www.quantumscape.com/technology/" }], color: "bg-slate-900", points: lang === 'en' ? ["Fast charge (80% in 15 mins)", "Inherent safety with zero thermal runaway", "Patent targets with solid-interface tech"] : ["極速快充（15分鐘內至 80%）", "本質安全架構，無熱失控風險", "擁有固-固界面處理技術之專利標的"] },
                    { title: t.sectors.s3_t[0], desc: lang === 'en' ? "R2R is the shared technical foundation for scaling and commoditizing all new materials. Producing batteries and displays like printing newspapers is the crown jewel of Industry 4.0." : (lang === 'zh-Hans' ? "R2R 是实现上述所有新材料规模化、平民化的共同技术底层。像印刷报纸一样生产电池与显示器，是工业 4.0 的核心皇冠。" : "R2R 是實現上述所有新材料規模化、平民化的共同技術底層。像印刷報紙一樣生產電池與顯示器，是工業 4.0 的核心皇冠。"), sources: [{ label: "VTT Printed Electronics & R2R", url: "https://www.vttresearch.com/en/ourservices/printed-electronics" }, { label: "AIMCAL Global Standards", url: "https://www.rolltoroll.org/" }], color: "bg-indigo-600", points: lang === 'en' ? ["Nano-precision coating & tension control", "Production costs reduced by 40-60%", "Equipment suppliers with tension control patents"] : ["納米級精度塗佈控制與超薄基材張力技術", "生產成本相較傳統工藝降低 40-60%", "掌握高精度張力控制與多層共擠技術的設備商"] },
                    { title: t.sectors.s2_t[0], desc: lang === 'en' ? "Modular hydrogen capsules solve the pain point of astronomical infrastructure costs. According to IEA, modular distribution will be the most economical path for de-carbonizing long-haul logistics and aviation." : (lang === 'zh-Hans' ? "氢能模块化胶囊技术解决了基础设施天价成本的痛点。根据 IEA 全球氢能评论，模块化分发将是长途物流与支线航空去碳化的最经济路径。" : "氫能模組化膠囊技術解決了基礎設施天價成本的痛點。根據 IEA 全球氫能評論，模組化分發將是長途物流與支線航空去碳化的最經濟路徑。"), sources: [{ label: "IEA Global Hydrogen Review 2024", url: "https://www.iea.org/reports/global-hydrogen-review-2024" }], color: "bg-emerald-600", points: lang === 'en' ? ["Avoid high-cost stations using logistics nets", "Premium for regional aero conversion kits", "Lightweight power integration tech"] : ["避開高成本加氫站，利用現有物流網配送", "支線航空改裝套件帶來的技術溢價", "模組化儲運膠囊及輕量化動力整合技術"] }
                ];
                return (
                    <div className="animate-in slide-in-from-right duration-700 pb-24 text-left font-black text-slate-900">
                        <section className="bg-slate-900 pt-32 pb-20 text-white text-left font-black">
                            <div className="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 text-left text-white font-black">
                                <button onClick={() => { setCurrentPage('home'); scrollToTop(); }} className="flex items-center gap-2 text-blue-400 font-bold mb-8 hover:text-blue-300 transition-colors uppercase tracking-widest text-xs font-black">
